Edition:
Quote: Some idea of 'cocksfoot fever' may be gleaned from the following extract from the Akaroa Mail of Friday, January 19, 1897 - 'The Monarch Cocksfoot absorbs all interest in the Peninsula this week, and nothing else is thought of, talked of, or worked at.'
